img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe535bb75442a8f8cb75751c19648b683e23000b","tid":156863,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T08:09:52.000Z","msg":"有冇戒埋口先?<br />\n依家我牛,海鮮,蛋都戒晒<br />\n唔知關唔關事<br />\n但我有食物敏感"},{"pid":"2f850e6823ba429c662c118150739f6ba9ac9bea","tid":156863,"uid":10071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T08:16:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇戒埋口先?<br />\n依家我牛,海鮮,蛋都戒晒<br />\n唔知關唔關事<br />\n但我有食物敏感</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n海鮮係指蟹、蝦嗰類定全部海鮮？<br />\n我睇醫生叫我淨係食魚同雞"},{"pid":"2fe63e980d9961db755a8de6d0d5c3eba5c17edb","tid":156863,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T08:20:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇戒埋口先?<br />\n依家我牛,海鮮,蛋都戒晒<br />\n唔知關唔關事<br />\n但我有食物敏感</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n海鮮係指蟹、蝦嗰類定全部海鮮？<br />\n我睇醫生叫我淨係食魚同雞</blockquote><br />\n蝦, 或者有殼個類掛<br />\n<br />\n不過我都好少食<br />\n一黎怕麻煩<br />\n二黎食完好明顯係會紅晒<br />\n<br />\n肉類得豬同雞囉<br />\n聽人講出黎曬多d太陽都對呢d有幫助<br />\n我自己就平時小小野都會去洗手<br />\n跟住俾個醫生叫我唔好再成日洗手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55999c6d3237aaf8ad03adac525aaf9da949b3f7","tid":156863,"uid":91503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T10:48:16.000Z","msg":"係咪有類固醇？"},{"pid":"63ea793d875a18c17a085a2f4e8a1c636ce2ef47","tid":156863,"uid":61284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T10:57:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我識人做屈人錢，佢幫我搵藥劑師配左隻膏搽<br />\n一兩日就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但唔知有冇得賣</blockquote><br />\n邊隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13e65244c31f399b0d5f778caadf39ede6f6d438","tid":156863,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T12:45:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquot